<collectingRegion box="[360,450,945,971]" country="Puerto Rico" name="Vieques" pageId="14" pageNumber="165">Vieques</collectingRegion>
Island and satellites, and western part of 
<collectingRegion box="[914,1003,945,971]" country="Puerto Rico" name="Culebra" pageId="14" pageNumber="165">Culebra</collectingRegion>
Island.
